    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dresses constructed so that panels cross over each other and can be fastened. These are of varied design and may be in any length and have a variety of sleeve types and necklines.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
